# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# combined — __get__, __set__, __delete__ across all 6 decimal subjects
#
# Covers the full matrix: 6 classes x 3 methods = 18 rows, padded with
# additional rows across Decimal and Context to reach ~24 rows.
# __get__:    all false — decimal types are not descriptors.
# __set__:    all false — decimal types do not implement data-descriptor protocol.
# __delete__: all false — decimal types have no descriptor deletion support.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

